-- Europe Better Prepared for Greek Euro Exit, Euro am Sonntag Says
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2012-06-10T12:56:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-10/europe-better-prepared-for-greek-euro-exit-euro-am-sonntag-says.html
Europe is better prepared than two
years ago to deal with a possible Greek exit from the 17-member
euro zone, an ally of German Chancellor  Angela Merkel  told  Euro
am Sonntag .  The change includes “the protection of the euro finance
sector outside Greece,” Michael Meister, the deputy caucus
leader of Merkel’s Christian Democratic Union in parliament, was
cited as saying by the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at 
